aiirs-artificial-intelligence-image-resi.name: AIIRS
aiirs-artificial-intelligence-image-resi.desc: Artificial Intelligence Image Resizer allows you to Add image size to crop image dynamically with using code & Remap Image Size.

broken-url-notifier\/broken-url-notifier.name: Broken Url Notifier
broken-url-notifier\/broken-url-notifier.desc: This plugin will send email to the site admin when there is broken url or Image.

cf7-international-sms-integration\/cf7-i.name: Contact Form 7 International Sms Integration
cf7-international-sms-integration\/cf7-i.desc: Works with the Contact Form 7 plugin to send SMS notifications when somebody submits your contact form, using the API Configured By Site Admin.

estimated-dispatch-date-woocommerce\/est.name: Estimated Dispatch Date For WooCommerce
estimated-dispatch-date-woocommerce\/est.desc: This plugin allows you to set, in days, how long a WooCommerce product takes before it is ready for disptach. It retrieves the estimated date for dispatch using the highest number in the order.

live-admin-customzier\/index.php.name: Live Admin Customizer
live-admin-customzier\/index.php.desc: Create Customized theme for wordpress admin panel. with out any code

product-brands-for-woocommerce\/product-.name: Product Brands For WooCommerce
product-brands-for-woocommerce\/product-.desc:
The brands extension for WooCommerce allows you to create brands for your shop; each brand can be named, described and assigned an image. Brands can then be:
  • Displayed as thumbnails on a page using a shortcode
  • Assigned to a product
  • Used to filter products using a special layered nav widget

sku-shortlink-for-woocommerce\/sku-short.name: SKU Shortlink For WooCommerce
sku-shortlink-for-woocommerce\/sku-short.desc: This handy plugin might just be what you have searched for. It will create URL Aliases for your WooCommerce products so you could still have your nicely Search Engine Optimized links and at the same time completely custom SKU based URLs for use in Social Media and e-quotes still linking to the same product.

wc-better-grouped-products\/wc-better-gr.name: WooCommerce Better Grouped Products
wc-better-grouped-products\/wc-better-gr.desc: Enrich your visitor with best grouped products view

wc-bulk-product-delete\/wc-bulk-product-.name: WC Bulk Product Delete
wc-bulk-product-delete\/wc-bulk-product-.desc: This simple plugin will be great tool if you want to bulk remove products from your Woocommerce shop by Deleting or just moving them to Bin.

wc-paytm-gateway\/wc-paytm-gateway.php.name: WC Paytm Gateway
wc-paytm-gateway\/wc-paytm-gateway.php.desc: Pay with Paytm is the simplest of the available ways to do payment integration to your website. It helps you create a no frills Payment button on your checkout page where amount can be fixed preconfigured on our servers or can be dynamic.

wc-previously-bought-product-notifier\/w.name: WC Previously Bought Product Notifier
wc-previously-bought-product-notifier\/w.desc: This plugin will display notifications to shop customers about products they have already bought before with information that is customization . Like order number, order date and custom text. Basic idea is to encourage customers to buy the same item again and again or the opposite, depending on what the shop is selling.

wc-product-stock-status\/wc-product-stoc.name: WC Product Stock Status
wc-product-stock-status\/wc-product-stoc.desc: This plugin is used to write the custom stock status with different colors for each woocommerce product or globally, let users to know exact stock status names in product details page.

wc-product-subtitle\/wc-product-subtitle.name: WooCommerce Product Subtitle
wc-product-subtitle\/wc-product-subtitle.desc:
WooCommerce Product Subtitle allows you to easily add a subtitle to your products. also provides various options to customize the output.
You can also use the shortcode [wc-ps] to display it within the post content or where ever you need.
It adds a simple input field right under the title field for products. It also add a subtitle column to the edit screen.

wc-user-role-based-coupon\/wc-user-role-.name: WC User Role Based Coupon
wc-user-role-based-coupon\/wc-user-role-.desc: This plugin extends the popular ecommerce Plugin Woocommerce so that users can be offered at different coupons for different customer groups.

woocommerce-attributes-menu-manager\/ind.name: WooCommerce Attributes Menu Manager
woocommerce-attributes-menu-manager\/ind.desc: Attributes (which can be used for the layered nav) are a custom taxonomy, meaning you can display them in menus, or display products by attributes.

woocommerce-bulk-attribute-manager\/wooc.name: Woocommerce Bulk Attribute Manager
woocommerce-bulk-attribute-manager\/wooc.desc: Manage bulk woocommerce product variations and attribute options. You will be able to choose from a list of product categories, and then choose which attributes to assign to the products.

woocommerce-quick-buy\/woocommerce-quick.name: Woocommerce Quick Buy
woocommerce-quick-buy\/woocommerce-quick.desc: Add Quick buy button to redirect user to checkout / cart immediately when he click quick buy button. When User Clicks This Button. The Current product Will Be Added To Cart And The User Will Be Redirected To Cart Page

woocommerce-quick-donation\/woocommerce-.name: WooCommerce Quick Donation
woocommerce-quick-donation\/woocommerce-.desc: WooCommerce Shopping Cart Donation which makes WooComerce to use for online donation purpose. This plugin will create a new product in the name of donation.

woocommerce-role-based-price\/woocommerc.name: WC Role Based Price
woocommerce-role-based-price\/woocommerc.desc: This plugin can make your simple WooCommerce shop in to multi currency and price level marketplace where products can be offered at different prices for different customer groups. Differentiate your registered users to get your shop more attractive. New roles can be created and managed.

woocommerce-single-product-checkout\/woo.name: WooCommerce Single Product Checkout
woocommerce-single-product-checkout\/woo.desc: Allows Shop Owners To Set Product To Be Sold Separately With Predefined Max Allowed Quantity & Min Required Quantity

wp-toobar-custom-link\/wp-toobar-custom-.name: WordPress ToolBar Custom Link
wp-toobar-custom-link\/wp-toobar-custom-.desc: The WordPress toolbar or admin bar is the menu that appears on the top of your admin area. This toolbar contains useful shortcuts to different admin screens in WordPress. You can customize it to add your own custom shortcuts in the toolbar for easy access.

wp-user-role-renamer\/wp-user-role-renam.name: WP User Role Renamer
wp-user-role-renamer\/wp-user-role-renam.desc: Set A Custom Or temporary name for wp user roles to make it eaiser for you to use the website

woocommerce-role-based-price-pro\/woocom.desc: This plugin can make your simple WooCommerce shop in to multi currency and price level marketplace where products can be offered at different prices for different customer groups. For example, Subscribers or Contributors get different prices than new customers. Differentiate your registered users to get your shop more attractive. New roles can be created and managed.
woocommerce-role-based-price-pro\/woocom.name: WooCommerce Role Based Pricing Pro

woocommerce-bulk-price-updater\/woocomme.desc: This plugin allows store owner / manager to update product prices by category in bulk. Prices can also be increased / decreased by Percentage (%) or fixed values, or Adding to / Subtracting from existing value. Price changes can be saved as templates and run quickly
woocommerce-bulk-price-updater\/woocomme.name: WooCommerce Bulk Price Updater

woocommerce-role-based-force-sell\/wooco.desc: The Role Based Force Sells extension allows you to link products together based on the user role, so they are added to the cart together. This is useful for linking a service or required product to another.
woocommerce-role-based-force-sell\/wooco.name: WooCommerce Role Based Force Sell

advanced-product-reviews-for-woocommerce.desc: Great product reviews can have a huge impact on driving customer sales, especially for items that are costly or unknown to your prospective customers. WooCommerce Advanced Product Reviews was designed to help your customers better review your products and help you sell more product.
advanced-product-reviews-for-woocommerce.name: Advanced Product Reviews For WooCommerce

wc-role-based-product-hiding\/wc-role-ba.desc:
An extension for WooCommerce, which allows you to hide products by user roles.
With this plugin, you can hide multiple products at once per role, by simply selecting selecting a user role based on per product / product category.
wc-role-based-product-hiding\/wc-role-ba.name: WooCommerce Role Based Product Hiding

woocommerce-role-based-up-cross-sell\/wo.desc: The Role Based UP / Cross Sells extension allows you to link products together based on the user role.
woocommerce-role-based-up-cross-sell\/wo.name: WooCommerce Role Based UP / Cross Sell

wc-role-based-payment-shipping-methods\/.desc:
Limit different user roles to specific payment / shipping methods
WooCommerce Role-Based Methods extension gives site administrators the ability to individually limit available Shipping Methods and Payment Gateways for each user role configured in WordPress.
wc-role-based-payment-shipping-methods\/.name: WooCommerce Role Based Payment / Shipping Methods

woocommerce-international-sms\/woocommer.desc:
This is a WooCommerce add-on. By Using this plugin admin and customers, can get notification about their order via SMS by using sms gateway
The WooCommerce International SMS plugin for WordPress is very useful when you want to get notified via SMS after placing an order. Buyer and seller both can get SMS notification after an order is placed. SMS notification options can be customized in the admin panel very easily
woocommerce-international-sms\/woocommer.name: WooCommerce International SMS

woocommerce-role-based-shipping-manager\.desc: WooCommerce Role-Based Manager extension gives site administrators the ability to individually limit available Shipping Methods and also allows administrator to set shipping methods price based on user role for each shipping method
woocommerce-role-based-shipping-manager\.name: WooCommerce Role Based Shipping Manager

wc-zip-pin-postal-code-validator\/wc-zip.desc: This WooCommerce plugin enables order restriction based on specific zip/post codes. You have to enter list of postcode in given area for which the order restriction works. When activated you will restrict selected gateways or billing address, shipping address and both address at checkout step based on specific zip/post codes.
wc-zip-pin-postal-code-validator\/wc-zip.name: WC Zip/Pin/Postal Code Validator

cf7-international-sms-integration-pro\/c.desc:
Works with the Contact Form 7 plugin to send SMS notifications when somebody submits your contact form, using the API Configured By Site Admin.
Adds an SMS box to your Contact Form 7 options pages, fill this in and you’ll get a text message each time somebody fills out one of your forms.
cf7-international-sms-integration-pro\/c.name: CF7 International SMS
